<h1><%= @prefab_store.name %> | $<%= @prefab_store.total_spent %></h1>

Tags:<br>
<% @prefab_store.tags.each do |tag| %>
    <%= link_to tag.name, user_tag_path(@user, tag) %>&nbsp
<% end %>
<br>
<br>

Carts:<br>
<% @prefab_store.carts.each do |cart| %>
    <%= link_to cart.note, user_cart_path(@user, cart) %>
    <br>
    <%= cart.date %> | <strong>$<%= cart.total %></strong>
    <br>
    <br>
<%end %>

<%= link_to 'Edit Store', edit_user_prefab_store_path(@user, @prefab_store) %>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Deleting the store is irreversible. If you recreate it, you will have to manually re-associate any carts that were previously associated with it.
So before clicking <%= link_to 'delete store', user_prefab_store_path(@user, @prefab_store), method: 'delete' %>, please make sure that you really want to do this.